description:
Where is there to go when the night is endless? (South Beach, Lincoln Rd) //

Photography + OBJ File Databending, 2015. Source image captured in Miami, Florida. "City of Vapors" began in 2015 as a speculative elegy capturing the spaces and vibes of growing up in Miami, a city that will one day sink into the sea. 

// Artwork by Sabato Visconti // // This is a special NFT drop as part of the Florence Night Out Pop-up Exhibition at Pivot Media in Florence, Massachusetts, September 25. This exhibit marks 10 years of creating glitch art // www.sabatobox.com // @sabatobox on IG //
